description:
You’ve heard of other flapping bird games, now play THE ORIGINAL FLAPPING BIRD GAME (flying high since 2012). Guide birds through trees and gobble-up tasty bees in this aerial adventure. Tap to flap!

This app offers in-app purchases. You may disable in-app purchasing using your device settings. See http://support.apple.com/kb/HT4213 for more info

“4/5…a solid title that’s more challenging than it looks.” – Touch Arcade

Easy to learn, a challenge to master, and satisfyingly addictive. Soar through the air with the tap of a finger. Keep tapping – or you’ll eat dirt (instead of bugs)!

LET’S FLY! START OFF AT YOUR BIRDHOUSE AND...

•Chomp evil bees from small to large for a bug feast! 
•Cruise through tree holes and dodge moving obstacles, like spiders, Venus fly traps, geysers, and more!
•Collect all 3 Stars in each level for a perfect score!
•Grab gears while you fly so you can unlock the dominating ...ROBOT BIRD! 
•Enjoy scenic fields, tree-filled forests, and tropical jungles – 45 levels in all! 
•Test your endurance with 3 Challenge modes.
•Bees got you beat? Get Kid Mode for a new canary bird and friendlier level of difficulty with 30 new levels.

Are you ready to take off? Come Fly With Me!
releaseNotes:
BIRD OF PARADISE? Update now and fly off into the sunset with an all-new Paradise environment.

Take a holiday and…

• Fly past volcanoes in 10 new twilight levels 
• Dodge our newest enemy: the Frog
• Test your mettle in a brand-new Robot Bird bonus level
• Toggle off messages and enjoy an uninterrupted flight
